dct_description_sm: Shows the western United States. Relief shown by hachures. At head of title: Map no. 10. In upper right-hand margin: 49. From R.C. Smith's Atlas of modern and ancient geography. New York, 1853. Prime meridians: Greenwich, Washington. "Entered according to Act of Congress in the year 1853 by Daniel Burgess & Co. ... "
dct_publisher_sm: New York : Daniel Burgess & Co., c1853.
